ensions and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewModifiers"},{"type":"text","text":" to apply tokens and styles on components and higher-level views."}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSuggestionChip":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is a UI element that allows to present recommended or predictive options based on user’s input or context,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"title":"OUDSSuggestionChip","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSuggestionChip/bodyDefaultSmall(_:)":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/bodyDefaultSmall(_:)","role":"symbol","title":"bodyDefaultSmall(_:)","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"bodyDefaultSmall","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract9OUDSThemeC","text":"OUDSTheme","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind